1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:08,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:04,000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:07,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:11,140
[Episode 27]

5
00:01:14,030 --> 00:01:15,500
It ends like this again.

6
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:17,810
Is this

7
00:01:18,270 --> 00:01:19,530
truly the end?

8
00:01:42,830 --> 00:01:43,450
Zhaomin.

9
00:01:46,750 --> 00:01:48,010
The detox pill I just gave you

10
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:49,060
is for countering demonic energy.

11
00:01:49,310 --> 00:01:51,170
It should be working by now.

12
00:01:51,600 --> 00:01:52,250
Any more left?

13
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:53,620
No.

14
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:56,340
I only got two from Elder Dongyang.

15
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:58,170
Too bad he's not here.

16
00:01:58,190 --> 00:01:58,890
What do we do now?

17
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:03,060
Let's find Master and the others.

18
00:02:11,670 --> 00:02:12,220
You go ahead.

19
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:13,370
I'm going to save Lifei.

20
00:02:13,670 --> 00:02:14,250
You...

21
00:02:17,670 --> 00:02:18,220
Fine.

22
00:02:18,550 --> 00:02:19,780
Zhaomin, be careful.

23
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:20,940
Don't draw any attention.

24
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,900
Wait until our backup arrives.

25
00:02:21,990 --> 00:02:22,460
Got it.

26
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:24,340
Zhaomin.

27
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,370
What is it?

28
00:02:29,590 --> 00:02:30,500
We'll talk later.

29
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,180
Just go save them.

30
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:44,650
Will you submit or not

31
00:02:45,830 --> 00:02:46,780
Huolian Abbey

32
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:48,570
will never side with demons!

33
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:12,180
You.

34
00:03:13,150 --> 00:03:13,740
Come here!

35
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:19,180
Qiongqi, come at me!

36
00:03:19,390 --> 00:03:19,970
Master!

37
00:03:22,150 --> 00:03:23,130
Hang in there!

38
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:32,370
Watch out!

39
00:03:45,270 --> 00:03:46,060
You're finally here!

40
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:59,410
Where did you hide the Lei Xiuyuan

41
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:01,650
who promised never to hurt me?

42
00:04:27,350 --> 00:04:27,980
Lifei.

43
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:30,810
I will never hurt you.

44
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,330
Lei Xiuyuan, let Lifei go!

45
00:04:56,030 --> 00:04:56,940
Zhaomin.

46
00:05:01,350 --> 00:05:02,130
Zhaomin!

47
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,740
You're not him.

48
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:07,860
You're not him.

49
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:10,250
You are Yecha!

50
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,890
You are Yecha!

51
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,890
Lifei, forgive me.

52
00:05:28,150 --> 00:05:29,540
Only by breaking through your seals

53
00:05:30,710 --> 00:05:32,250
can I truly protect you.

54
00:06:54,590 --> 00:06:55,660
You've fully shed your shell.

55
00:06:57,470 --> 00:06:59,180
No one can ever hurt you again.

56
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,420
Not even me.

57
00:08:06,710 --> 00:08:07,420
This time,

58
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,300
I kept my word.

59
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:15,790
♪The warmth within my arms♪

60
00:08:16,170 --> 00:08:19,210
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

61
00:08:19,510 --> 00:08:22,910
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

62
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:23,890
Xiuyuan.

63
00:08:23,890 --> 00:08:26,540
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

64
00:08:26,910 --> 00:08:30,110
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

65
00:08:30,430 --> 00:08:33,630
♪I can no longer tell you♪

66
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:37,230
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

67
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:40,550
♪Utter that line♪

68
00:08:40,910 --> 00:08:42,630
♪Knowing love and hate♪

69
00:08:42,950 --> 00:08:46,870
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

70
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:49,830
♪I still linger on♪

71
00:08:50,230 --> 00:08:54,430
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

72
00:08:54,830 --> 00:08:59,190
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

73
00:08:59,470 --> 00:09:02,430
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

74
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:06,190
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

75
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:09,670
♪I wish you well♪

76
00:09:09,990 --> 00:09:11,670
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

77
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:15,160
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

78
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:15,780
No.

79
00:09:17,310 --> 00:09:18,950
♪You're still screaming♪

80
00:09:19,230 --> 00:09:22,560
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

81
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:23,380
No!

82
00:09:23,990 --> 00:09:28,230
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

83
00:09:28,590 --> 00:09:30,510
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

84
00:09:30,510 --> 00:09:31,610
No!

85
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:38,240
♪Leaping straight into that heartbreaking past♪

86
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:42,680
♪Just to keep you safe♪

87
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:50,690
♪My breath is about to stop♪

88
00:09:50,810 --> 00:09:54,330
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

89
00:09:54,450 --> 00:09:57,890
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

90
00:09:58,050 --> 00:10:00,840
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

91
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,630
♪I smile as it ends♪

92
00:10:02,630 --> 00:10:04,940
No! No!

93
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:08,440
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

94
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:12,000
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

95
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:15,480
♪To light your way through the night♪

96
00:10:15,610 --> 00:10:17,330
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

97
00:10:17,490 --> 00:10:21,320
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

98
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,850
No!

99
00:10:22,850 --> 00:10:24,720
♪You're still screaming♪

100
00:10:24,880 --> 00:10:29,240
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

101
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:34,090
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

102
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:35,970
Xiuyuan!

103
00:10:35,970 --> 00:10:37,290
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

104
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:39,600
♪I'd shatter my soul♪

105
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:44,560
♪To lay all your days in peace♪

106
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:46,560
♪Who says that love and hate♪

107
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:51,680
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped?♪

108
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:53,760
♪I will level the seas and mountains♪

109
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:58,400
♪Break the waves, no matter how mad it seems♪

110
00:10:58,750 --> 00:11:03,160
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

111
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:06,400
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

112
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:12,720
♪With the light from my fingertips, I build a paradise♪

113
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:17,080
♪To wander with you♪

114
00:11:22,920 --> 00:11:23,450
Ye.

115
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:24,420
How is it?

116
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,260
- Are you okay? - Lu?

117
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:27,450
Lu?

118
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:33,260
Gelin?

119
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,850
You talked about forever.

120
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:36,380
What would I do if you died?

121
00:11:37,350 --> 00:11:37,940
Gelin.

122
00:11:38,990 --> 00:11:39,330
I...

123
00:11:39,590 --> 00:11:40,300
Don't say anything.

124
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:41,850
Just stay alive.

125
00:11:48,160 --> 00:11:49,330
Look. What is it?

126
00:11:51,230 --> 00:11:52,420
The demonic energy has all been purified by it.

127
00:12:05,510 --> 00:12:06,060
Lifei.

128
00:12:07,680 --> 00:12:08,210
Lifei!

129
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:09,970
Where are you hurt?

130
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:14,810
I killed Xiuyuan.

131
00:12:16,110 --> 00:12:17,330
That's Xiuyuan's blood?

132
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:19,540
Did you...?

133
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:22,570
What happened?

134
00:12:24,110 --> 00:12:24,970
He's dead.

135
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,210
- Lifei! - Zhaomin.

136
00:12:33,510 --> 00:12:34,300
Calm down.

137
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,090
This isn't your fault.

138
00:12:37,470 --> 00:12:38,260
It's all my fault.

139
00:12:40,990 --> 00:12:42,380
I should be the one dead.

140
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:43,330
No.

141
00:12:43,870 --> 00:12:44,420
No.

142
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:46,300
He deserved to die.

143
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:48,140
He was a demon.

144
00:12:49,110 --> 00:12:50,060
Our enemy.

145
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:00,780
Zhaomin.

146
00:13:03,710 --> 00:13:04,210
Zhaomin!

147
00:13:04,990 --> 00:13:05,610
Zhaomin!

148
00:13:06,350 --> 00:13:06,970
Zhaomin!

149
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:07,940
Zhaomin.

150
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,090
Zhaomin!

151
00:13:14,470 --> 00:13:15,180
Who did this?

152
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:16,850
Who killed Zhaomin?

153
00:13:21,870 --> 00:13:22,810
It was me.

154
00:13:29,710 --> 00:13:30,900
It's all my fault.

155
00:13:40,710 --> 00:13:42,090
The Divine Tree colluded with the Demon Lord

156
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,850
to overthrow the immortal sects.

157
00:13:44,350 --> 00:13:45,060
Seize her!

158
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:52,330
Your Highness,

159
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,210
what do you mean by this?

160
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:55,850
She's a demon!

161
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:08,090
If she hadn't used the Divine Tree's power

162
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:09,090
to purify the demonic energy,

163
00:14:09,830 --> 00:14:10,690
you would all have been

164
00:14:11,280 --> 00:14:12,570
killed by the demons.

165
00:14:13,560 --> 00:14:14,730
But she is the Divine Tree.

166
00:14:15,560 --> 00:14:16,490
The demon attack

167
00:14:16,870 --> 00:14:17,900
happened because of her.

168
00:14:18,400 --> 00:14:19,540
She's a walking disaster.

169
00:14:20,230 --> 00:14:21,020
Who's the disaster?

170
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:26,420
Wasn't today's fiasco enough?

171
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,450
If you hadn't coveted the Divine Tree

172
00:14:28,560 --> 00:14:29,610
and insisted on that public trial,

173
00:14:30,230 --> 00:14:32,660
Wuyue Court wouldn't have been caught off guard!

174
00:14:33,350 --> 00:14:33,970
And Elder Guangwei,

175
00:14:34,560 --> 00:14:35,020
Zhaomin,

176
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:37,140
and so many others wouldn't have...

177
00:14:45,800 --> 00:14:47,020
This demon attack

178
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:48,810
has severely wounded the immortal sects.

179
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:50,940
We don't know what the Demon Lord has planned next.

180
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,020
I suggest

181
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:54,330
you all return

182
00:14:54,470 --> 00:14:55,420
and tend to your wounds.

183
00:14:56,110 --> 00:14:59,380
Don't give the demons another opening.

184
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:01,610
We'll discuss

185
00:15:02,350 --> 00:15:03,330
everything else later.

186
00:15:05,870 --> 00:15:07,330
Xingzheng Hall was wiped out long ago!

187
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:08,540
Why should we listen to you?

188
00:15:13,350 --> 00:15:14,730
Everyone, stay still! Behave!

189
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:24,090
Xingzheng Hall

190
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:27,420
fell victim to Zong Quan, who colluded with demons.

191
00:15:28,110 --> 00:15:29,020
Though we suffered losses,

192
00:15:29,870 --> 00:15:31,420
we still stand unbroken.

193
00:15:32,590 --> 00:15:35,810
Can't you all learn from that?

194
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:38,450
Fine.

195
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:40,090
Defending against the demons matters.

196
00:15:40,920 --> 00:15:42,090
Thank you for the reminder, Your Highness.

197
00:15:42,630 --> 00:15:43,690
We're leaving.

198
00:15:44,560 --> 00:15:45,300
- Go! - Go.

199
00:16:07,160 --> 00:16:11,050
[In Memory of Zhaomin]

200
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:16,090
Lifei, wake up.

201
00:16:18,590 --> 00:16:20,730
Lifei, wake up!

202
00:16:21,470 --> 00:16:23,490
Carry yourself like a girl.

203
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,140
Be graceful and proper.

204
00:16:25,510 --> 00:16:26,780
No more clumsiness.

205
00:16:26,920 --> 00:16:27,690
Understand?

206
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:31,300
Lifei.

207
00:16:32,990 --> 00:16:33,730
Take care.

208
00:16:44,990 --> 00:16:45,780
Zhaomin,

209
00:16:47,710 --> 00:16:49,140
I'll listen to you from now on.

210
00:16:51,230 --> 00:16:52,450
Please don't be mad at me.

211
00:17:04,360 --> 00:17:05,580
Zhaomin loved you so much.

212
00:17:07,790 --> 00:17:09,010
She wouldn't be mad at you.

213
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:16,560
[In Memory of Zhaomin]

214
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:18,860
Zhaomin.

215
00:17:20,960 --> 00:17:21,660
I bought

216
00:17:21,990 --> 00:17:23,820
these for you in Duanming City.

217
00:17:24,990 --> 00:17:26,820
Peepshow scrolls,

218
00:17:27,750 --> 00:17:28,770
assorted preserved fruits,

219
00:17:29,550 --> 00:17:30,580
and lotus incense.

220
00:17:31,840 --> 00:17:33,450
I always wanted to give them to you.

221
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,940
But I never had the courage.

222
00:17:47,310 --> 00:17:48,580
I'll go check on Master.

223
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:13,040
[In Memory of Guangwei]

224
00:18:16,360 --> 00:18:18,490
Here, Guangwei.

225
00:18:19,510 --> 00:18:20,140
Drink.

226
00:18:28,600 --> 00:18:29,340
Master,

227
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,770
you're hurt. You shouldn't drink.

228
00:18:34,160 --> 00:18:34,940
Besides,

229
00:18:36,200 --> 00:18:37,450
Elder Guangwei was aloof

230
00:18:38,270 --> 00:18:39,100
and serious.

231
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:41,180
He probably didn't like wine.

232
00:18:41,790 --> 00:18:43,010
Bring him tea next time.

233
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:45,820
Since when did you start fussing over people?

234
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:48,940
You're becoming more and more like Zhaomin.

235
00:18:53,030 --> 00:18:54,250
Did you go see Zhaomin?

236
00:19:00,470 --> 00:19:01,420
If it weren't for saving me,

237
00:19:02,790 --> 00:19:04,180
Zhaomin wouldn't have died.

238
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:06,050
It's all my fault.

239
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:08,380
First, Master.

240
00:19:10,710 --> 00:19:12,100
Then Elder Guangwei.

241
00:19:13,640 --> 00:19:14,490
Zhaomin.

242
00:19:15,640 --> 00:19:16,690
And Xiuyuan.

243
00:19:17,470 --> 00:19:19,250
I used to call him a jinx.

244
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:21,690
Turns out I'm the real jinx.

245
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:29,580
Alright.

246
00:19:30,600 --> 00:19:31,730
Stop overthinking.

247
00:19:33,160 --> 00:19:34,180
You and Xiuyuan

248
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:36,380
were both caught up in fate.

249
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:37,860
Some things

250
00:19:38,750 --> 00:19:39,690
are hard to explain.

251
00:19:41,710 --> 00:19:43,210
But one thing is clear.

252
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:45,660
They all wanted you to live well.

253
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:48,420
Don't let them down.

254
00:19:50,230 --> 00:19:51,050
Elder Guangwei?

255
00:19:52,270 --> 00:19:53,690
Was it him who woke Xiuyuan?

256
00:19:56,990 --> 00:19:58,180
Guangwei

257
00:19:58,200 --> 00:20:00,010
used the last of his strength.

258
00:20:00,710 --> 00:20:02,340
He channeled the Heart-Cleansing Art

259
00:20:03,030 --> 00:20:04,250
into Xiuyuan's forehead.

260
00:20:05,600 --> 00:20:06,620
The Heart-Cleansing Art?

261
00:20:07,270 --> 00:20:08,250
It can

262
00:20:09,360 --> 00:20:12,180
dissolve the demon's Soul-Bewitching Vines.

263
00:20:12,710 --> 00:20:14,620
In the last Sea Calamity,

264
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:15,690
we saw too many of the monsters

265
00:20:15,710 --> 00:20:17,420
infected by those vines.

266
00:20:17,990 --> 00:20:19,290
They lost themselves,

267
00:20:19,710 --> 00:20:20,860
just like Xiuyuan,

268
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:22,770
and became violent and bloodthirsty.

269
00:20:25,120 --> 00:20:26,380
But you know

270
00:20:26,920 --> 00:20:28,660
that wasn't Xiuyuan's true self.

271
00:20:31,550 --> 00:20:32,340
I know.

272
00:20:34,550 --> 00:20:36,100
But I still killed him.

273
00:20:38,710 --> 00:20:39,450
In that moment,

274
00:20:40,270 --> 00:20:42,180
I gave it everything I had to kill him.

275
00:20:44,880 --> 00:20:46,140
He'd rather die by my hand

276
00:20:47,990 --> 00:20:49,530
than hurt me.

277
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:59,730
If you're hurting, just cry.

278
00:21:00,550 --> 00:21:02,660
You'll feel better.

279
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,530
Master.

280
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:10,180
I'm so scared.

281
00:21:11,710 --> 00:21:13,050
I'm afraid of dragging more of you down.

282
00:21:15,230 --> 00:21:17,140
Afraid of watching more people die before me.

283
00:21:19,550 --> 00:21:21,050
I can't take it anymore.

284
00:21:22,470 --> 00:21:23,380
I liked you better

285
00:21:23,710 --> 00:21:25,180
the way you used to be.

286
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:27,530
You were so carefree.

287
00:21:28,840 --> 00:21:29,730
If you ask me,

288
00:21:30,120 --> 00:21:31,140
life and death are just fate.

289
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:32,140
Let things take their course.

290
00:21:32,470 --> 00:21:35,050
Don't carry everything on your own shoulders.

291
00:21:35,710 --> 00:21:37,530
The Sea Calamity looms, and human hearts run deep.

292
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:40,660
You've already severed your worldly ties.

293
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:42,900
Why not just leave?

294
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:44,860
Find a place to live in seclusion,

295
00:21:45,310 --> 00:21:46,860
just like Qingcheng.

296
00:21:47,440 --> 00:21:48,450
I believe

297
00:21:49,120 --> 00:21:49,970
there must be a place for you

298
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:52,380
in this vast world.

299
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:56,690
I'm the Divine Tree after all.

300
00:21:58,230 --> 00:22:00,140
There's no place for me in this life.

301
00:22:19,790 --> 00:22:20,420
Your Highness.

302
00:22:20,600 --> 00:22:21,210
Mr. Luo.

303
00:22:22,710 --> 00:22:23,690
You're still here?

304
00:22:25,200 --> 00:22:26,860
I'm worried about the safety of the immortal sects.

305
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:27,900
I can neither eat nor sleep.

306
00:22:28,120 --> 00:22:28,970
After much thought,

307
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:30,180
I'd like to share

308
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:31,900
some honest words with you.

309
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:34,450
Mr. Luo, go on.

310
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:37,900
After the battle at Wuyue Court,

311
00:22:38,030 --> 00:22:39,250
the immortal sects are badly weakened

312
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:40,380
and divided.

313
00:22:40,510 --> 00:22:41,970
They're in no shape to fight the demons again.

314
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:44,580
But your influence is at its peak.

315
00:22:45,030 --> 00:22:47,290
And the Divine Tree trusts you completely.

316
00:22:47,710 --> 00:22:48,490
I believe

317
00:22:48,750 --> 00:22:50,940
you could use the Divine Tree to command the world.

318
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:54,860
Lifei is the disciple of Elder Qingcheng and Elder Chongyi,

319
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:57,530
and my closest friend.

320
00:22:58,160 --> 00:23:00,380
Anyone who schemes against her or tries to harm her

321
00:23:01,360 --> 00:23:03,140
is my enemy.

322
00:23:04,120 --> 00:23:05,010
No matter who they are,

323
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:06,730
I will slaughter their entire clan

324
00:23:07,400 --> 00:23:08,340
to the very last.

325
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:12,730
Guess I spoke out of turn.

326
00:23:13,470 --> 00:23:14,290
Alright then.

327
00:23:14,790 --> 00:23:15,490
I'm leaving.

328
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:16,290
See yourself out.

329
00:23:26,640 --> 00:23:27,970
Ungrateful fool.

330
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,580
I offer you good counsel,

331
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:30,490
and you reject it.

332
00:23:31,400 --> 00:23:32,770
If I weren't wounded,

333
00:23:32,790 --> 00:23:34,250
you'd never get to claim the Divine Tree

334
00:23:34,360 --> 00:23:35,580
and lord it over me.

335
00:23:36,230 --> 00:23:36,730
Who's there?

336
00:23:40,600 --> 00:23:41,530
You?

337
00:23:46,550 --> 00:23:48,340
Patrols must be tightened this time.

338
00:23:48,790 --> 00:23:49,940
If the Divine Tree appears,

339
00:23:50,310 --> 00:23:51,580
capture it alive.

340
00:23:52,360 --> 00:23:53,140
Go patrol.

341
00:23:55,470 --> 00:23:56,010
Guardian,

342
00:23:56,470 --> 00:23:57,340
has the Lord awakened?

343
00:24:00,360 --> 00:24:01,180
Why isn't he awake yet?

344
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:05,490
Everyone is waiting.

345
00:24:06,120 --> 00:24:06,940
If he never wakes up...

346
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:07,620
Qiongqi!

347
00:24:10,470 --> 00:24:11,180
Guardian,

348
00:24:11,510 --> 00:24:12,730
we've lain low for centuries.

349
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:14,180
We've come so far.

350
00:24:14,790 --> 00:24:16,050
We have to have a backup plan.

351
00:24:16,230 --> 00:24:17,050
Think of all our people.

352
00:24:17,230 --> 00:24:18,050
Are we supposed to

353
00:24:18,070 --> 00:24:19,340
just wait here forever?

354
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:22,620
If the Lord hadn't been too soft

355
00:24:23,270 --> 00:24:24,420
to absorb the Divine Tree,

356
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:25,690
it wouldn't have come to this.

357
00:24:25,710 --> 00:24:26,340
Silence!

358
00:24:28,160 --> 00:24:29,820
The Lord will not die.

359
00:24:30,230 --> 00:24:30,860
Yes.

360
00:24:31,270 --> 00:24:32,530
The Lord is the supreme ruler of our clan.

361
00:24:32,990 --> 00:24:34,820
He'll never be defeated by those petty immortals!

362
00:24:58,400 --> 00:24:59,940
He's a little demon.

363
00:25:00,310 --> 00:25:02,250
I need to kill him!

364
00:25:04,070 --> 00:25:04,820
Even if he's the Demon Lord,

365
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:06,530
he's still a life.

366
00:25:10,550 --> 00:25:11,210
Besides,

367
00:25:11,880 --> 00:25:13,340
he's returned to his original state now.

368
00:25:14,470 --> 00:25:15,940
There's no good or evil in him.

369
00:25:22,070 --> 00:25:22,530
Here.

370
00:25:24,120 --> 00:25:25,250
You won't eat radish porridge.

371
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:26,620
And you spit out the sweet potato.

372
00:25:27,070 --> 00:25:29,180
This is milk I stole

373
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:30,380
from that tiger.

374
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:31,380
Just try a little.

375
00:25:36,360 --> 00:25:37,770
What do you even want?

376
00:25:50,400 --> 00:25:51,250
You two...

377
00:25:53,600 --> 00:25:55,380
You two were meant to be together.

378
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:03,730
Master,

379
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:05,770
why hasn't he grown

380
00:26:05,790 --> 00:26:07,140
in all these centuries?

381
00:26:07,550 --> 00:26:08,660
[Young Hu Jiaping]
Is he some kind of monster?

382
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:11,010
Don't talk nonsense.

383
00:26:11,400 --> 00:26:11,860
Go.

384
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:13,860
Deliver this letter to Chufeng Academy.

385
00:26:19,680 --> 00:26:20,940
Resentment is a net,

386
00:26:22,230 --> 00:26:23,490
trapping both user and prey.

387
00:26:24,710 --> 00:26:25,970
Only by breaking free

388
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:27,860
can the soul find peace.

389
00:26:37,510 --> 00:26:38,690
Graceful as bamboo,

390
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:39,900
virtue known afar.

391
00:26:40,470 --> 00:26:41,140
From now on,

392
00:26:41,550 --> 00:26:43,530
your name will be Lei Xiuyuan.

393
00:26:45,960 --> 00:26:46,380
Here.

394
00:26:46,600 --> 00:26:47,690
Pay your respects to the Crown Prince.

395
00:26:49,030 --> 00:26:50,900
Greetings, Your Royal Highness.

396
00:26:52,310 --> 00:26:53,140
No need for formalities.

397
00:26:53,710 --> 00:26:54,490
My name is Ye Ye.

398
00:26:54,600 --> 00:26:56,340
Let's study and play together

399
00:26:56,360 --> 00:26:57,100
from now on.

400
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:09,690
No way?

401
00:27:10,510 --> 00:27:11,900
Me? Acting Sect Leader?

402
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:14,050
We old ones are either wounded

403
00:27:14,550 --> 00:27:15,250
or broken.

404
00:27:15,680 --> 00:27:17,940
You younger ones are either too badly hurt

405
00:27:17,990 --> 00:27:19,380
or still too inexperienced.

406
00:27:21,990 --> 00:27:22,660
So,

407
00:27:23,030 --> 00:27:24,380
you are

408
00:27:24,710 --> 00:27:25,860
the best choice.

409
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:27,970
I'm the worst choice.

410
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:30,210
Sir,

411
00:27:30,600 --> 00:27:31,770
you know me.

412
00:27:31,990 --> 00:27:32,820
I... I'm

413
00:27:33,120 --> 00:27:34,050
naturally lazy.

414
00:27:34,510 --> 00:27:35,490
I really can't do it.

415
00:27:37,470 --> 00:27:38,380
You think

416
00:27:38,710 --> 00:27:39,770
you're lazier than me?

417
00:27:39,990 --> 00:27:41,050
You want to talk about being lazy?

418
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:43,290
You have a strong sense of right and wrong.

419
00:27:43,710 --> 00:27:45,250
You're chivalrous and courageous.

420
00:27:45,990 --> 00:27:47,580
You don't follow the crowd.

421
00:27:49,230 --> 00:27:51,290
That's more than enough.

422
00:27:52,270 --> 00:27:53,820
We trust you

423
00:27:54,400 --> 00:27:55,340
to be the acting Sect Leader.

424
00:27:55,400 --> 00:27:56,690
This is wrong.

425
00:27:59,030 --> 00:27:59,940
Xiguang.

426
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,420
Master.

427
00:28:02,310 --> 00:28:04,380
It's our fault.

428
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,820
At the critical moment,

429
00:28:07,270 --> 00:28:08,690
we're all too wounded and weak

430
00:28:08,710 --> 00:28:09,860
to take care of ourselves.

431
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:12,100
We have no choice but to place this heavy burden

432
00:28:13,120 --> 00:28:14,730
on you.

433
00:28:15,510 --> 00:28:16,100
Master!

434
00:28:16,550 --> 00:28:17,940
Please. I can't accept this.

435
00:28:18,230 --> 00:28:18,730
Master.

436
00:28:19,230 --> 00:28:19,730
Master.

437
00:28:20,310 --> 00:28:21,490
I'm not capable enough.

438
00:28:22,360 --> 00:28:23,340
I'm ashamed.

439
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:24,620
Ma'am.

440
00:28:25,270 --> 00:28:25,900
Master.

441
00:28:26,360 --> 00:28:27,340
Don't say that.

442
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:29,580
I've been a terrible disciple.

443
00:28:30,030 --> 00:28:32,010
It's easy

444
00:28:32,030 --> 00:28:32,820
to change that.

445
00:28:33,440 --> 00:28:34,290
Just agree to be

446
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:35,530
the acting Sect Leader.

447
00:28:37,790 --> 00:28:38,380
Alright.

448
00:28:38,840 --> 00:28:41,970
I'll notify everyone as soon as possible.

449
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:44,580
Do a good job.

450
00:28:59,310 --> 00:28:59,940
Zhaomin,

451
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:03,730
I never thought the nightmare I had on Fanghu Island would come true.

452
00:29:04,360 --> 00:29:06,860
They actually want me to be acting Sect Leader.

453
00:29:07,310 --> 00:29:07,730
I...

454
00:29:09,880 --> 00:29:11,380
It's not that I'm scared.

455
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:12,140
I...

456
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:16,490
Fine. I'm just scared.

457
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:19,620
I'm afraid I won't do a good job.

458
00:29:20,270 --> 00:29:21,340
You know me.

459
00:29:22,070 --> 00:29:23,820
I'm a free spirit.

460
00:29:23,840 --> 00:29:26,420
I can't handle this kind of responsibility.

461
00:29:30,270 --> 00:29:31,730
I have no choice now.

462
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:34,210
I'm planning to sneak down the mountain tonight.

463
00:29:34,230 --> 00:29:35,380
I'll run far away.

464
00:29:35,990 --> 00:29:37,940
Let them find another disciple for this position.

465
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:44,380
I thought you'd be reliable in a crisis.

466
00:29:45,880 --> 00:29:47,770
Never expected you to disappoint me so much!

467
00:29:58,200 --> 00:29:58,970
If you run,

468
00:29:59,360 --> 00:30:00,860
who will protect Lifei, Simo,

469
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:02,140
and the other juniors?

470
00:30:02,680 --> 00:30:05,050
Who will look after the injured elders?

471
00:30:06,360 --> 00:30:07,010
Xiguang,

472
00:30:07,790 --> 00:30:09,380
you've run away once before.

473
00:30:10,230 --> 00:30:11,100
Don't run

474
00:30:11,360 --> 00:30:12,970
and hide again this time.

475
00:30:21,270 --> 00:30:21,820
Zhao...

476
00:30:31,550 --> 00:30:32,380
Zhaomin!

477
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:34,290
Don't worry!

478
00:30:37,030 --> 00:30:37,940
I'll take good care of them

479
00:30:39,710 --> 00:30:40,620
for you.

480
00:30:44,640 --> 00:30:46,010
Deng may seem unreliable,

481
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:47,770
but he's thoughtful,

482
00:30:47,990 --> 00:30:48,900
honorable,

483
00:30:49,160 --> 00:30:50,010
and far better than most.

484
00:30:50,960 --> 00:30:52,010
Wuyue Court will thrive

485
00:30:52,400 --> 00:30:53,490
under his leadership.

486
00:30:55,550 --> 00:30:56,770
You seem to be in better spirits

487
00:30:57,270 --> 00:30:58,380
these past few days.

488
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:02,450
Staying a broken mess

489
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:04,420
would only worry Master

490
00:31:04,750 --> 00:31:05,690
and everyone else.

491
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,290
I don't want to be a burden.

492
00:31:10,790 --> 00:31:11,940
Being with you is a blessing,

493
00:31:12,360 --> 00:31:13,530
if anything.

494
00:31:17,360 --> 00:31:17,940
Lifei.

495
00:31:18,790 --> 00:31:19,530
I know

496
00:31:20,070 --> 00:31:21,580
you've been grieving over Xiuyuan.

497
00:31:23,230 --> 00:31:23,900
But

498
00:31:24,510 --> 00:31:25,580
Rakshasa took him away.

499
00:31:26,360 --> 00:31:27,820
Maybe he's still alive.

500
00:31:43,550 --> 00:31:45,180
The Fragrance Bond is gone.

501
00:31:47,120 --> 00:31:48,420
He's really not here anymore.

502
00:31:58,230 --> 00:31:58,770
Lifei.

503
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:00,380
Let the past

504
00:32:00,600 --> 00:32:01,250
stay in the past.

505
00:32:02,120 --> 00:32:03,180
Think about the people

506
00:32:03,790 --> 00:32:05,100
still by your side.

507
00:32:09,120 --> 00:32:09,620
Oh,

508
00:32:10,270 --> 00:32:11,250
how's Ye Ye?

509
00:32:11,710 --> 00:32:13,900
He was badly hurt saving me that day.

510
00:32:15,790 --> 00:32:17,140
I haven't seen him in days.

511
00:32:17,710 --> 00:32:18,620
Wasn't he taken away

512
00:32:18,990 --> 00:32:20,180
by Sect Leader Miao?

513
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:23,690
Changyue and Ye Ye wouldn't just leave without a word.

514
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:25,490
Could something have happened?

515
00:32:26,710 --> 00:32:27,580
Don't panic.

516
00:32:28,310 --> 00:32:30,100
Maybe he was wounded and unconscious,

517
00:32:30,440 --> 00:32:32,010
and the Dizang Sect disciples took him back.

518
00:32:32,470 --> 00:32:33,210
I'll send someone to ask.

519
00:32:33,680 --> 00:32:34,140
Alright.

520
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:42,860
Lifei,

521
00:32:43,230 --> 00:32:44,100
Master said you need to

522
00:32:44,270 --> 00:32:44,970
drink this medicine.

523
00:32:46,550 --> 00:32:47,450
Thanks.

524
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,450
I haven't seen Master all afternoon.

525
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:51,770
Where did he go?

526
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:53,900
He went to Hushe Peak.

527
00:33:31,790 --> 00:33:33,380
The horn of the Si beast.
[*Divine one-horned animal]

528
00:33:36,510 --> 00:33:37,250
Master!

529
00:33:42,070 --> 00:33:42,690
Master.

530
00:33:43,710 --> 00:33:44,770
What are you doing here?

531
00:33:46,840 --> 00:33:47,770
I want to

532
00:33:48,360 --> 00:33:49,620
fix this place up.

533
00:33:50,360 --> 00:33:51,900
Look how messy it is.

534
00:33:54,030 --> 00:33:54,820
Let me do it.

535
00:33:56,200 --> 00:33:57,450
Back in Qingqiu,

536
00:33:57,750 --> 00:33:59,860
the little cabin often got battered by the wind.

537
00:34:00,270 --> 00:34:01,290
I was always the one fixing it.

538
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:05,290
I can't believe Qingcheng

539
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:08,050
made you do all that work.

540
00:34:11,630 --> 00:34:12,260
Sit down.

541
00:34:16,070 --> 00:34:17,090
That's nothing.

542
00:34:18,190 --> 00:34:19,970
That old man had all sorts of quirks.

543
00:34:20,760 --> 00:34:22,090
He bragged without blinking an eye.

544
00:34:22,590 --> 00:34:24,650
He lost nearly every time he gambled.

545
00:34:25,990 --> 00:34:27,420
Stingy and greedy.

546
00:34:27,960 --> 00:34:29,820
All day he just lay in his chair,

547
00:34:30,110 --> 00:34:31,380
smoking and dozing off.

548
00:34:31,720 --> 00:34:32,860
He was lazy

549
00:34:33,240 --> 00:34:34,530
and picky about everything.

550
00:34:35,760 --> 00:34:37,570
It was always something, like the radish being too bland

551
00:34:37,800 --> 00:34:39,220
or the tea being too hot.

552
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:41,650
He...

553
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:46,570
But

554
00:34:48,150 --> 00:34:50,220
our days were always so joyful

555
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:52,130
and lively.

556
00:34:52,630 --> 00:34:53,650
We lived better than immortals.

557
00:34:56,110 --> 00:34:59,380
All these years, Qingcheng had you by his side.

558
00:35:00,720 --> 00:35:03,260
That's why he got to live such a happy life.

559
00:35:05,590 --> 00:35:07,010
I should thank you for him.

560
00:35:15,070 --> 00:35:16,420
I'm the one who owes him.

561
00:35:19,150 --> 00:35:20,450
He did so much for me.

562
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:23,130
But I never gave anything back.

563
00:35:24,030 --> 00:35:25,090
What are you saying?

564
00:35:25,840 --> 00:35:27,260
You gave plenty.

565
00:35:27,510 --> 00:35:28,860
He ate so much of your delicious cooking

566
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:30,010
over the years.

567
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:33,650
Simo is always talking

568
00:35:34,240 --> 00:35:36,450
about your chicken and mushroom stew.

569
00:35:38,440 --> 00:35:39,860
Have you seen

570
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:40,820
Simo lately?

571
00:35:42,070 --> 00:35:42,780
No.

572
00:35:44,280 --> 00:35:45,340
Simo's missing?

573
00:35:45,720 --> 00:35:46,780
Haven't seen him lately.

574
00:35:50,150 --> 00:35:51,610
Well, Master,

575
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:52,940
I'll fix the cabin.

576
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:54,900
You're still hurt.

577
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:56,490
Get some rest.

578
00:35:56,960 --> 00:35:57,780
I'll be back soon.

579
00:36:07,470 --> 00:36:08,490
Leaving already?

580
00:36:13,760 --> 00:36:14,940
Qingcheng,

581
00:36:16,590 --> 00:36:19,570
Lifei really takes after you.

582
00:36:31,510 --> 00:36:32,170
Qingcheng.

583
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:36,450
That kid's still as mischievous as ever.

584
00:37:19,670 --> 00:37:20,530
Qingcheng, Guangwei.

585
00:37:22,720 --> 00:37:27,260
The child you two fought so hard to protect...

586
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:37,090
I hope...

587
00:37:39,670 --> 00:37:44,650
I hope she has fewer hardships ahead.

588
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:52,570
I asked the guards.

589
00:37:53,030 --> 00:37:54,010
When the demons retreated,

590
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:55,130
Ye Ye and Simo

591
00:37:55,150 --> 00:37:56,610
went after them.

592
00:37:57,240 --> 00:37:57,970
They haven't come back.

593
00:37:58,880 --> 00:37:59,970
That was days ago.

594
00:38:00,760 --> 00:38:01,900
Could the demons have found them?

595
00:38:04,070 --> 00:38:05,420
Ye Ye carried a message talisman.

596
00:38:05,630 --> 00:38:06,700
If anything had happened,

597
00:38:06,880 --> 00:38:08,050
he would've let us know.

598
00:38:08,990 --> 00:38:10,090
Since we haven't heard anything,

599
00:38:10,510 --> 00:38:12,130
they probably haven't found the demons yet.

600
00:38:15,720 --> 00:38:16,700
Demons are vicious.

601
00:38:17,550 --> 00:38:18,650
Better if they don't find them.

602
00:38:19,360 --> 00:38:20,530
Zhaomin is already gone.

603
00:38:21,030 --> 00:38:22,090
If Simo and the others...

604
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:25,220
I've already sent people to search.

605
00:38:25,470 --> 00:38:26,780
We'll hear something soon.

606
00:38:29,510 --> 00:38:30,420
I'll go look again.

607
00:38:54,990 --> 00:38:55,740
My Lord.

608
00:38:58,510 --> 00:38:59,260
My Lord.

609
00:39:02,960 --> 00:39:04,700
Your old friends followed us here.

610
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:07,220
Qiongqi is entertaining them.

611
00:39:11,760 --> 00:39:13,450
It's been seven full days.

612
00:39:13,920 --> 00:39:16,050
My Lord, when will you wake up?

613
00:39:19,990 --> 00:39:20,780
I know

614
00:39:22,280 --> 00:39:24,970
the last person you want to hurt is Jiang Lifei.

615
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:30,420
I'll bring her to you.

616
00:39:35,190 --> 00:39:36,420
Any news from your side?

617
00:39:38,190 --> 00:39:39,570
The disciples I sent haven't reported back.

618
00:39:39,590 --> 00:39:40,820
We can't find Ye Ye

619
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:41,970
or the others either.

620
00:39:42,110 --> 00:39:42,970
Where could they have gone?

621
00:39:42,990 --> 00:39:43,420
Wait.

622
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:44,490
There's demonic energy.

623
00:39:55,670 --> 00:39:56,860
It's Ye Ye and the others' swords.

624
00:39:58,590 --> 00:40:00,700
If you don't want Ye Ye and his two companions to die,

625
00:40:01,400 --> 00:40:02,610
trade Jiang Lifei for them

626
00:40:03,110 --> 00:40:04,340
tomorrow at Chen hour

627
00:40:05,030 --> 00:40:06,820
outside Lilie Valley.

628
00:40:08,670 --> 00:40:09,820
So they're there.

629
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:11,610
I'm going now.

630
00:40:12,590 --> 00:40:13,260
Don't rush.

631
00:40:14,550 --> 00:40:15,610
Demons are cunning and treacherous.

632
00:40:16,030 --> 00:40:17,420
This could be a trap.

633
00:40:19,360 --> 00:40:19,940
You're right.

634
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:20,970
Alright then.

635
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:23,050
I'll go scout things out.

636
00:40:23,590 --> 00:40:24,260
Everyone else

637
00:40:24,510 --> 00:40:25,260
stays put.

638
00:40:26,880 --> 00:40:27,380
And

639
00:40:27,990 --> 00:40:29,450
don't tell Jiang Lifei.

640
00:40:59,150 --> 00:40:59,700
Excuse me.

641
00:41:00,470 --> 00:41:01,570
Where can I find Deng?

642
00:41:01,590 --> 00:41:02,780
She got so many disciples killed.

643
00:41:03,070 --> 00:41:03,820
How dare she show up?

644
00:41:04,030 --> 00:41:04,900
She's not even human.

645
00:41:05,510 --> 00:41:06,050
What a plague.

646
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:06,900
Let's go.

647
00:41:18,630 --> 00:41:20,300
Your Highness, your internal injuries haven't healed.

648
00:41:20,470 --> 00:41:21,740
Don't go to Lilie Valley.

649
00:41:23,920 --> 00:41:24,450
Tongzhou.

650
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:26,490
Did you find Ye Ye and the others?

651
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:28,420
Are they in Lilie Valley?

652
00:41:29,070 --> 00:41:30,260
Someone spotted them nearby.

653
00:41:30,800 --> 00:41:32,130
Deng Xiguang has already gone to check.

654
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:33,700
Then I need to go too.

655
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:38,610
What's wrong?

656
00:41:39,720 --> 00:41:40,610
Old injury flaring up?

657
00:41:41,630 --> 00:41:42,650
You need to be careful.

658
00:41:43,150 --> 00:41:43,780
Let me see.

659
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:45,900
I'm fine.

660
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:08,940
Sorry.

661
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:11,090
I have to get stronger

662
00:42:11,800 --> 00:42:12,940
to protect you.

663
00:42:16,190 --> 00:42:16,940
Come here.

664
00:42:20,590 --> 00:42:21,170
Your Highness!

665
00:42:27,440 --> 00:42:28,940
Your spirit energy came from Lifei.

666
00:42:30,190 --> 00:42:31,420
Only by drawing on her spirit energy

667
00:42:32,440 --> 00:42:33,450
can you help me.

668
00:42:38,050 --> 00:42:38,780
[The Eternal Fragrance]

669
00:42:38,780 --> 00:42:40,560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

670
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:57,020
♪The warmth within my arms♪

671
00:42:57,180 --> 00:43:00,700
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

672
00:43:00,820 --> 00:43:04,340
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

673
00:43:04,460 --> 00:43:07,940
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

674
00:43:07,940 --> 00:43:11,580
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

675
00:43:11,980 --> 00:43:15,260
♪I can no longer tell you♪

676
00:43:15,380 --> 00:43:18,900
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

677
00:43:18,940 --> 00:43:21,940
♪Utter that line♪

678
00:43:22,100 --> 00:43:24,140
♪Knowing love and hate♪

679
00:43:24,220 --> 00:43:28,620
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

680
00:43:29,340 --> 00:43:31,420
♪I still linger on♪

681
00:43:31,580 --> 00:43:35,860
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

682
00:43:36,020 --> 00:43:40,540
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

683
00:43:40,620 --> 00:43:44,140
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

684
00:43:44,220 --> 00:43:47,660
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

685
00:43:47,940 --> 00:43:51,180
♪I wish you well♪

686
00:43:51,340 --> 00:43:53,060
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

687
00:43:53,220 --> 00:43:57,900
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

688
00:43:58,500 --> 00:44:00,580
♪You're still screaming♪

689
00:44:00,740 --> 00:44:05,220
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

690
00:44:05,340 --> 00:44:09,820
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

691
00:44:10,060 --> 00:44:13,020
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

692
00:44:13,140 --> 00:44:15,020
♪Leaping straight into♪

693
00:44:15,140 --> 00:44:19,900
♪That heartbreaking past♪

694
00:44:20,140 --> 00:44:23,660
♪Just to keep you safe♪

695
00:44:30,100 --> 00:44:33,420
♪My breath is about to stop♪

696
00:44:33,540 --> 00:44:37,060
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

697
00:44:37,180 --> 00:44:40,620
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

698
00:44:40,780 --> 00:44:43,980
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

699
00:44:44,100 --> 00:44:47,820
♪I smile as it ends♪

700
00:44:47,980 --> 00:44:51,620
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

701
00:44:51,820 --> 00:44:55,220
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

702
00:44:55,380 --> 00:44:58,500
♪To light your way through the night♪

703
00:44:58,580 --> 00:45:00,620
♪Knowing love and hate♪

704
00:45:00,700 --> 00:45:05,100
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

705
00:45:05,860 --> 00:45:07,900
♪I still linger on♪

706
00:45:08,060 --> 00:45:12,340
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

707
00:45:12,500 --> 00:45:17,020
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

708
00:45:17,100 --> 00:45:20,300
♪Torn inside, still I burn bright♪

709
00:45:20,500 --> 00:45:22,460
♪With the light from my fingertips♪

710
00:45:22,540 --> 00:45:26,940
♪I build a paradise♪

711
00:45:27,100 --> 00:45:30,580
♪To wander with you♪
